{"tid":1004660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳橋二死三傷工業意外　三承建商罰 13 萬至 26 萬　家屬不滿","createTime":"2019-02-01T15:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T15:50:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"192fcc97e9e21ef0d89d655ce41bf969eac25f5f","tid":1004660,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋前年一宗工業意外，造成兩死三傷，三間承建商今日在西九龍裁判法院，分別被判罰款 13 萬至 26 萬，有到庭旁聽的家屬認為判罰過輕，感到不滿及失望，認為政府應立法加強規管保障工人安全，亦應該罰他們永久禁止投標政府工程。<br />\n<br />\n事發在 2017 年 3 月 29 日，工人在港珠澳大橋接線工程，拆卸一個升降裝置吊著的臨時工作台時，升降裝置橫樑突然倒塌，兩條吊着工作台的吊索折斷，工作台的三名工人墮海，橋面兩個工人就被塌下的橫樑，造成兩死三傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3 家承建商香港寶嘉建築有限公司、中國港灣工程有限責任公司，及威勝利香港有限公司，被控違反《職業安全及健康條例》、《建築地盤（安全）規例》等，分別判罰款 264,000 元、214,000 元和 136,000 元。</span>裁判官判刑時形容案件是悲劇，海上工作危險，工人完全靠承建商提供安全工作環境，三間承建商事後雖然被禁接政府工程一年，但在建築界仍有永久角色，法庭要向社會傳遞，保障工人安全的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/港珠澳橋二死三傷工業意外-三承建商罰-13-萬至-26-萬-家屬不滿/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E6%A9%8B%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%89%E5%82%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-%E4%B8%89%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%95%86%E7%BD%B0-13-%E8%90%AC%E8%87%B3-26-%E8%90%AC-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%2F&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxssg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=66ddde23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E6%A9%8B%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%89%E5%82%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-%E4%B8%89%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%95%86%E7%BD%B0-13-%E8%90%AC%E8%87%B3-26-%E8%90%AC-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%2F&h=1be4cf0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/港珠澳橋二死三傷工業意外-三承建商罰-13-萬至-26-萬-家屬不滿/</a><br />\n<br />\n死兩個人，賠六十幾萬搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b57f3c5e51e8d61d0d0de9147261abf9b306c5","tid":1004660,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b44628753d11820aaead29fcb2a88ffcef84af8","tid":1004660,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61fab649c156f35ab0f327112ff942b04a2b4db","tid":1004660,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"橋面兩個工人就被塌下的橫樑，造成兩死三傷。<br />\n漏咗d字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1033d1aaa1624c117116f7d85648b75b52dc332e","tid":1004660,"uid":771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"呢個係罰比政府喎<br />\n<br />\n工傷致死有勞工保險另計<br />\n<br />\n疏忽有犯法就保險公司再追番大判"},{"pid":"aae61a43f0e8603ce7f4ee5b8d2b44a92d32eb50","tid":1004660,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"修橋補路無屍骸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b959ee0c1820286402ca2801e884c0baf93aaba6","tid":1004660,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1033d1aaa1624c117116f7d85648b75b52dc332e","tid":1004660,"uid":771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"呢個係罰比政府喎<br />\n<br />\n工傷致死有勞工保險另計<br />\n<br />\n疏忽有犯法就保險公司再追番大判"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"84 個月"}]}